extendedInfo.description: The Worms family lived happyly taking long walks along the praire until.....the angry birds kidnapped the worms mother. Desperately she tells her children to look for Super Nelson who was the only zombie on earth capable of rescuing her.Following their mother's advice the worms go to the graveyard to unbury the salvator. After several hours of hard work, the could finally take Nelson out of his tomb. Though Super Nelson considered this an almost impossible mission he promised the worms to save their mother.If you like classic arcade games like Ghost 'n Goblins, Altered Beast, Wonder Boy, Rainbow Island, bubble bobble then you will enjoy Super Zombie.
